src="http://p3.pstatp.com/large/3c5f000296d8890c9a4f" img_width="570" img_height="322" alt="世界最美女拳王：如果你能打赢我，那么就能娶我回家！" inline="0"></p><p><img src="http://p9.pstatp.com/large/3c660000d5899b9491b7" inline="0"></p><p>由于实力强劲，同时长相漂亮、身材火辣，伊卡翠娜在世界范围内都拥有很高的人气，更是不乏追求者。对此，伊卡翠娜曾说过：“想娶我，那就得先打败我。”作为打泰拳出身的运动员，伊卡翠娜和泰拳王播求也十分熟悉。他们不仅多次单独训练，私交也很不错。</p><p><img src="http://p3.pstatp.com/large/3c600002976d826942aa" img_width="465" img_height="374" alt="世界最美女拳王：如果你能打赢我，那么就能娶我回家！" inline="0"></p><p>对于美丽的伊卡翠娜，播求一直十分心动，并且曾主动追求过她，但最终抱憾而归。细心的拳迷应该发现了，伊卡翠娜今年很少出现在公众视野中，原来她在2月份的时候就传出怀有身孕，并且已经嫁给了当地的一个修车厂老板。</p></div>

In recent years, boxing has become one of the most talked about sports, martial arts, Kunlun and other games is very popular, China also gave birth to many excellent boxing champion, such as Zou City Ming, a dragon, Li Jingliang and others. Relatively speaking, women's boxing is much less concerned about, but there is a female boxing champion is world-renowned, that is, from the Russian beauty boxer - Icatrina van der Wava.

Icatna was born in 1991, the height of 1 meter 7,16 years old in order to test the police and began to practice boxing, from the out of control. At the same time she was a Thai boxing master, had to get amateur Muay Thai champion and the Belarusian Muay Thai champion. Because of the amazing beauty, bodybuilding slender figure and blue charming eyes, Icahitna known as "boxing Taiwan Barbie", soon became popular in the world boxing.

At the age of 18, Icatna began to dominate amateur boxing, she not only successfully get IFMA amateur champion, and 3 times to complete the defending. Since then for four consecutive years won the Belarusian women's Muay Thai champion, swept the amateur league, Icatna decided to formally enter the professional boxing.

With extraordinary strength, Icatna in the professional boxing industry also made a remarkable record. In 2012, Icatna won a 2-game winning streak in a 54kg career Muay Thai match. In 2013, Icaztina went to South Korea to challenge Li Yiyuan, and finally beat Lee with a smooth attack, to know that before Lee made 20 games undefeated. But Icatna also have a time when the stage in Kunlun has lost to China "KO Queen" Wang Ke Han. Last year Icah Rina has played a game in Nanjing, she beat the Chinese teenager Zeng Xiaoting, Zeng Xiaoting's brow was broken, blood DC.

Due to the strength of strong, while looks beautiful, hot body, Icatna in the world have a high popularity, but there is no lack of suitors. In this regard, Icatna had said: "want to marry me, it would have to first beat me." As a boxing fist of the athletes, Icahitas and Thai boxing king broadcast is also very familiar with. They are not only a few separate training, personal friendship is also very good.

For the beautiful Ikatuo Na, broadcast has been very heart, and has taken the initiative to pursue her, but eventually regret and return. Careful boxing fans should be found, Icahitas rarely appear in the public eye this year, when she was born in February when pregnant pregnant, and has been married to a local garage owner.
